        "caption": "Literature data for Sapaki. Coordinates, parallaxes, proper motions, and G-band photometry were retrieved from Gaia Data Release 3 (Gaia Collaboration \\citeyear{Gaia2022}). The $B-$ and $V$-band photometry values were taken from the TESS Input Catalog V8.2 (Paegert et al. \\citeyear{Petal2021}). $J$-, $H$- and $K_{s}$-band photometry was taken from the 2MASS Point Source Catalog (Skrutskie et al. \\citeyear{Setal2006}). W1-band and W2-band photometry values were taken from the WISE All-Sky Data Release (Cutri et al. \\citeyear{Cetal2012}), while the [8.0] $\\mu$m photometry was taken from the GLIMPSE Source Catalog (Benjamin et al. \\citeyear{Betal2003})",
